D

DisabledOnOs - Annotation Type in org.junit$pioneer.jupiter
@DisabledOnOs is used to signal that the annotated test class or test method is disabled on the specified operating systems.

E

EnabledOnOs - Annotation Type in org.junit$pioneer.jupiter
@EnabledOnOs is used to signal that the annotated test class or test method is disabled on all operating systems except the specified ones.
